latestPosts.caption:
Who needs a glass when you’ve got the whole bottle and room service? 🍷😉
@oakwoodpremiermelbourne 

Our stay at @oakwoodpremiermelbourne was nothing short of amazing 😍 From the moment we walked in, it was 5-star service, stunning views, and total relaxation 😌 

🛏️ The rooms were spacious, modern, and came with all the comforts. 
🍷 We loved unwinding with room service and wine (clearly!)
🌇 The panoramic views of the city and Port Phillip Bay? Breathtaking.
🍸 The Lobby Bar was the perfect spot for a cheeky evening drink
💪 And the gym? Fully equipped, just in case we got too comfy 😅
🎮 Also a games room which was so fun.

With South Melbourne Market, Southbank, and the CBD right nearby, the location couldn’t be better!

Want to experience it too?
Use SOCIALS15 for 15% off all room types, valid until 30 Dec 2025 when you book via discoverasr.com/OPM 💻

Thank you so much for having us 😘
